{"tid":1388511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家隨身攜帶「基本個人防護裝備」","createTime":"2019-07-30T17:06:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T17:20:49.000Z","uid":7277,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"12730b6c1eef3e5a8ecb32d523cea57336101d41","tid":1388511,"uid":7277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:06:03.000Z","msg":"大家都知道 基本上依家所有活動<br />\n只要有狗 就一定好大機會有衝突<br />\n希望大家唔好再抱住僥倖嘅心態<br />\n因為你永遠唔會知啲狗癲起上嚟會做啲乜<br />\n好似今晚葵涌警署咁<br />\n冇啦啦比人拎椒噴你你點頂？<br />\n<br />\n個袋長期準備定基本個人防護裝備係一定冇死嘅<br />\n就算比狗搜身發現都入你唔到<br />\n呢啲護具只係保護自己 唔係啲乜嘢武器<br />\n如果覺得頂安全帽太阻地方<br />\n起馬都隨身帶定眼罩同冰袖<br />\n普通口罩就唔使講啦<br />\n藍絲同狗周圍影相 <br />\n除咗屌佢地影相<br />\n大家保護好自己唔比人影到先係最重要<br />\n袋定幾個士啤嘅 <br />\n見到其他人冇可以即刻比佢 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c9974e32ed7704c99d59cf36b8b7f42a9c49817","tid":1388511,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:13:18.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErY1NGl2p_M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DErY1NGl2p_M&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kaooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=1f7d81c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErY1NGl2p_M</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwGX_Vgq-1G0&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kaooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=4f50310a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0</a><br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港！時代革命！<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong! <br />\nThe Revolution Of Our Times! </span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>五大訴求</strong></span></span></ins><br />\n 1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n 2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n 3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n 4. 追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>Hongkongers 5 Demands:</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n1. Full Withdrawal of the Extradition Bill<br />\n2. Retraction of the Characterisation of the Protestas a Riot<br />\n3. Release all Arrested Protesters<br />\n4. Accountability for Police and Yuen Long White Shirts Brutality<br />\n5. Implement Dual Universal Suffrage"},{"pid":"71fef341abda50c20031032409b14a4a696929c7","tid":1388511,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:16:03.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"05b6b87d265d3617ab69362ff7459fcf723eef32","tid":1388511,"uid":274934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:18:45.000Z","msg":"借個位黎擺擺 <br />\n入黎簽左佢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入黎簽左佢 斷popo武器<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1388013\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1388013</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"520faab81a45a1497a9229cc4f2761e6f5565009","tid":1388511,"uid":194894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:19:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a0fa990a90fe0648509872883baea261094cfdc","tid":1388511,"uid":194894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:20:29.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n    唔好去瑪嘉烈<br />\n【緊急！】唔好去瑪記，就算入都唔好上外科病房<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1388350\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1388350</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港需要你<br />\n我地都係香港人，我願意罷工</span></span><img src=\"